📘 API Reference – HubSpot CRM: Contacts Integration 🔐 Authentication <p>Authorization header:</p> <pre><code>Authorization: Bearer YOUR_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN</code></pre> 📥 Check for Existing Contact <p>Endpoint: <code>GET /crm/v3/objects/contacts?email={email}</code></p> <p>Headers:</p> <pre><code>Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN</code></pre> <p>Description:   Перевіряє, чи існує контакт із зазначеним email у CRM.</p> <p>Example Response (no match):</p> <pre><code>{
  "results": []
}</code></pre> <p>Example Response (contact found):</p> <pre><code>{
  "results": [
    {
      "id": "123456789",
      "properties": {
        "email": "john.doe@example.com",
        "firstname": "John"
      }
    }
  ]
}</code></pre> 📝 Create New Contact <p>Endpoint: <code>POST /crm/v3/objects/contacts</code></p> <p>Headers:</p> <pre><code>Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_PRIVATE_APP_TOKEN</code></pre> <p>Request Body:</p> <pre><code>{
  "properties": {
    "firstname": "John",
    "lastname": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "phone": "+380991112233",
    "source": "web_form"
  }
}</code></pre> <p>Success Response:</p> <pre><code>{
  "id": "987654321",
  "message": "Contact created successfully.",
  "properties": {
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "firstname": "John"
  }
}</code></pre> <p>Error Response (Duplicate):</p> <pre><code>{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Contact already exists"
}</code></pre>
